The calculation of the semiconductor band gap was expressed by the following equation:7αhvn=C(hv-Eg)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
